\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363474\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363474</a><br />\n與此同時,LIHKG香港女神總會盃非聯賽參賽女神提名亦都已經展開,截止提名期為17年9月4日0時,淨返兩日左右咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d83586c3f7c5d59874a41e2813e7dce738333a","tid":383702,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"其他巴打都黎推下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吹下水都可以架,成40頁,大把quota講野<br />\n但如果得我講既話,個post就上唔到頂,上唔到頂既話其他巴打就可能投唔到票<br />\n佢地投唔到票既話就會好可惜,好可惜既話我都會好傷心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deaef017a1f14644536e260892ea923a7741aae4","tid":383702,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BQO46Cg.png?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBQO46Cg.png%3F1&h=7b0d1827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/im86eA8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fim86eA8.png&h=ff18d360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家聽日會抽少少時間一齊觀賞首季環球女神冠軍盃分組賽既抽籤儀式啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n實際時間我會喺開始前再喺telegram果邊仲有連登開即討post交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTHX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.g